## Problem
FileStore fails when `.body` file exceeds 2GB, causing IO Error, stuck MsgSeqNum, and Acceptor can't send message out.

```
FIX::FileStoreFactory acceptorFileStoreFactory(acceptorSettings);
FIX::FileLogFactory acceptorFileLogFactory(acceptorSettings);
m_acceptor = new FIX::SocketAcceptor(*m_acceptorApp, acceptorFileStoreFactory, acceptorSettings, acceptorFileLogFactory);
```

<img width="1506" height="870" alt="filestore-bug-bigfile" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b26a3246-edce-4e96-8d69-4172c081be1e" />

## Solution
I have updated FileStore fseek, ftell to 64-bit version for MSVC and add `-D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64` for Unix platform.

